    <item>
      <title>Newmont 以 4.25 亿美元的价格将加拿大矿山出售给 Discovery Silver</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/newmont-sells-canadian-mine-to-discovery-silver-for-425-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽蒙特公司将以高达 4.25 亿美元的价格出售其位于安大略省的 Porcupine 金矿，该公司正在推进收购 Newcrest Mining Ltd. 后的资产剥离计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/newmont-sells-canadian-mine-to-discovery-silver-for-425-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:40:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将注入 180 亿美元现金以填补巨大的流动性缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行计划向国内金融系统注入近 180 亿美元，加大力度缓解现金短缺问题。印度现金短缺问题达到十多年来的最高水平，一些人认为这损害了亚洲第三大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:27:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
