    <item>
      <title>特朗普的快速贸易行动扰乱市场，油价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对特朗普政府迅速采取的贸易举措做出反应，油价在涨跌之间波动，美国先是威胁对哥伦比亚实施一系列限制措施，随后又推迟了这一决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 23:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，各大石油公司开启财报季，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普也大谈美国的化石燃料潜力。西非的可可问题增加了再次出现供应短缺的风险。尽管价格暴跌，但这家全球最大的钴矿商仍计划继续生产这种电池金属。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
